    <briefdescription>
<para>AVX Q4_K x Q8_K matvec kernel for Sandy/Ivy Bridge. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Uses _mm_maddubs_epi16 (SSSE3) for efficient u8*s8 multiply-add while maintaining our scale format from unpack_q4_k_scales.</para>
<para>Key improvement over SSE: _mm_maddubs_epi16 processes 16 pairs per instruction vs SSE&apos;s _mm_cvtepu8_epi16 + _mm_madd_epi16 (8 pairs). </para>
    </detaileddescription>
